---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About David Krug — 701am"
  description="Founder of 701am. An earned-media operator based in Singapore, with a long history of building in higher-education lead gen, performance SEO, and the systems that make data-driven press repeatable."
  pageType="aboutPage"
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
    { name: 'About' },
  ]}
>

  <article class="ab">

    <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         MASTHEAD — Hi, I'm David
         ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <header class="ab-mast">
      <p class="ab-mast-eyebrow">Section II · About Me · Singapore</p>

      <h1 class="ab-mast-h">
        Hi! I'm <em>David</em> Krug.
      </h1>

      <p class="ab-mast-lede">
        I'm an earned-media operator and builder based in Singapore. I have two amazing daughters — <em>Sofia</em>, born 2017, and <em>Dana</em>, born 2025 — who keep the office honest and the writing fast.
      </p>

      <p class="ab-mast-lede">
        I run a small studio called <a href="/" class="ab-link">701am</a>, where I find the un-ignorable angle inside public data and place it where it cannot be denied. I write the dispatches, build most of the technical infrastructure myself, and sit with founders at sunrise.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         § 01 — BACKGROUND
         ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="ab-section">
      <header class="ab-section-head">
        <p class="ab-section-label">§ 01 · Background</p>
        <h2 class="ab-section-h">My <em>story.</em></h2>
      </header>

      <div class="ab-prose">
        <p>
          I came up in performance content. Starting in 2007, I spent the better part of two decades operating in the higher-education lead-generation space — building and running properties that connected prospective students with online and traditional programs. <a href="https://collegeranker.com" class="ab-link">CollegeRanker.com</a>, the original incarnations of <em>CollegeChoice.net</em>, <em>BestCollegeReviews.com</em>, and roughly a hundred others. I consulted on <em>TheBestSchools.org</em>. The work taught me a lot about SEO; more importantly, it taught me where attention actually lives and what makes a publisher worth visiting twice.
        </p>

        <p>
          In 2019 I joined a <em>Manhattan-based agency</em> as Director of SEO, where the specialty was producing infographics for tech and startup clients — visual stories built to earn coverage, not to win pop-up traffic. A year later, in 2020, I took the same title at a <em>private-equity-backed publishing portfolio</em> covering legal, financial, and insurance. Both jobs shaped how I think about narrative and distribution today.
        </p>

        <p>
          On the side, I had been building. In 2017 I started <em>PressTitan</em>, a managed-WordPress hosting agency that grew steadily and quietly until I sold it in 2026. In 2021 I launched <a href="https://quoteyeti.com" class="ab-link">QuoteYeti.com</a>. In 2025 I built <a href="https://mbastack.org" class="ab-link">MBAStack.org</a> as a modern take on graduate-program guides. Most of these still run.
        </p>

        <p>
          The exit from PressTitan in 2026 cleared the runway for what I had quietly been building for a decade: a small, opinionated office for earned media. <a href="/" class="ab-link">701am</a> is the result. It is named after the minute after the alarm — 7:01 a.m. — when a hundred million people decide what matters today, and the press cycle begins again.
        </p>

        <p>
          Alongside 701am I keep a few other things alive: the original education properties, the <a href="/skills" class="ab-link">Earned Media Skills</a> open-source library, and a handful of internal tools that exist because the office needed them. Most of what I build I build in public. The rest I write about <a href="/notes" class="ab-link">in the dispatches</a>.
        </p>

        <div class="ab-aphorism">
          ★ Generic is a form of dishonesty ★
        </div>

        <p>
          When I'm not at the desk, I'm with my daughters, or losing badly at chess. I write best at sunrise, ship at midnight, and believe — strongly and unfashionably — that the open web is still the most interesting commercial real estate on the internet.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Timeline -->
      <div class="ab-timeline" aria-label="Career timeline">
        <p class="ab-timeline-label">Timeline</p>
        <ol class="ab-timeline-list">
          <li>
            <span class="ab-time-year">2007</span>
            <span class="ab-time-event">Started in higher-education lead gen — CollegeChoice.net, BestCollegeReviews.com, and ~100 other properties</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ab-time-year">2017</span>
            <span class="ab-time-event">Sofia is born; founded PressTitan, a managed-WordPress hosting agency</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ab-time-year">2019</span>
            <span class="ab-time-event">Director of SEO at a Manhattan agency specializing in tech-startup infographics</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ab-time-year">2020</span>
            <span class="ab-time-event">Director of SEO at a P/E-backed legal, financial &amp; insurance publishing portfolio</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ab-time-year">2021</span>
            <span class="ab-time-event">Launched QuoteYeti.com</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ab-time-year">2025</span>
            <span class="ab-time-event">Dana is born; launched MBAStack.org</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ab-time-year">2026</span>
            <span class="ab-time-event">Exited PressTitan; launched 701am — the earned-media office</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ab-time-year">Now</span>
            <span class="ab-time-event">Building the Workshop, and the Earned Media Skills library, and the dispatches</span>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         § 02 — CONNECT
         ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="ab-section ab-section--connect">
      <header class="ab-section-head">
        <p class="ab-section-label">§ 02 · Connect</p>
        <h2 class="ab-section-h">Find me <em>online.</em></h2>
      </header>

      <p class="ab-connect-deck">
        These are the only accounts that are mine. If you see another, it is not me.
      </p>

      <ul class="ab-connect-list">
        <li>
          <a href="https://x.com/realdavidkrug" class="ab-connect-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener me">
            <span class="ab-connect-name">X <em>@realdavidkrug</em></span>
            <span class="ab-connect-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/davidpkrug.bsky.social" class="ab-connect-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener me">
            <span class="ab-connect-name">Bluesky <em>@davidpkrug</em></span>
            <span class="ab-connect-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/davidpaulkrug/" class="ab-connect-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener me">
            <span class="ab-connect-name">LinkedIn <em>in/davidpaulkrug</em></span>
            <span class="ab-connect-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/701am" class="ab-connect-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener me">
            <span class="ab-connect-name">GitHub <em>@701am</em></span>
            <span class="ab-connect-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/contact" class="ab-connect-link">
            <span class="ab-connect-name">Write to the desk <em>directly</em></span>
            <span class="ab-connect-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         § 03 — WHAT I BUILD AT 701AM
         ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="ab-section">
      <header class="ab-section-head">
        <p class="ab-section-label">§ 03 · The office</p>
        <h2 class="ab-section-h">What I'm building <em>at 701am.</em></h2>
      </header>

      <p class="ab-builds-deck">
        Three things live behind the masthead. <em>The Skills</em> are for your AI agent. <em>The Scroll</em> is for you. <em>The Build workshop</em> is for the morning you have a meeting and nothing to say in it.
      </p>

      <div class="ab-builds">

        <a href="/skills" class="ab-build">
          <p class="ab-build-num">i.</p>
          <h3 class="ab-build-h">Earned Media Skills</h3>
          <p class="ab-build-deck">
            An open-source library of twenty-eight markdown skills your AI agent can read. Pitch craft, journalist research, the humanizer. <em>MIT licensed.</em>
          </p>
          <span class="ab-build-cta">Browse the skills <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></span>
        </a>

        <a href="/legend-maker" class="ab-build">
          <p class="ab-build-num">ii.</p>
          <h3 class="ab-build-h">The Scroll</h3>
          <p class="ab-build-deck">
            The full earned-media method, written down. Method, pitch, placement. The same playbook the office uses, <em>given away.</em>
          </p>
          <span class="ab-build-cta">Read the scroll <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></span>
        </a>

        <a href="/build" class="ab-build ab-build--featured">
          <span class="ab-build-ribbon">★ Free workshop ★</span>
          <p class="ab-build-num">iii.</p>
          <h3 class="ab-build-h">Build a Data Story</h3>
          <p class="ab-build-deck">
            Five questions. Two public datasets. <em>One headline you did not have yesterday.</em> A three-minute workshop that ends with a strategy memo on your screen.
          </p>
          <span class="ab-build-cta">Open the workshop <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></span>
        </a>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         § 04 — DISPATCHES
         ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="ab-section ab-section--dispatches">
      <header class="ab-section-head">
        <p class="ab-section-label">§ 04 · Writing</p>
        <h2 class="ab-section-h">Read the <em>dispatches.</em></h2>
      </header>

      <div class="ab-dispatches-body">
        <p class="ab-dispatches-p">
          The blog at 701am is called <em>the dispatches</em> — a running record of essays and field notes on earned media, attention, authority, and the work of being remembered. I file most of them at sunrise. <em>You can read them; you can subscribe; you can ignore them.</em>
        </p>

        <div class="ab-dispatches-cta">
          <a href="/notes" class="ab-cta-primary">
            Read the dispatches <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/rss.xml" class="ab-cta-secondary">
            Subscribe by RSS
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

   <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         CODA — sign off
         ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <footer class="ab-coda">
      <p class="ab-coda-stamp">★ Colophon ★</p>
      <p class="ab-coda-p">
        This site is set in <em>Newsreader</em> and Instrument Sans. Built with Astro on a quiet Saturday. Filed from Singapore, every morning at 7:01am.
      </p>
      <p class="ab-coda-sig">— David</p>
    </footer>

  </article>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     /about — personal page in 701am editorial voice
     ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .ab {
    max-width: 56rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--x1) 32px calc(var(--x1) + var(--x1));
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .ab-link {
    color: var(--ink);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--claret);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
    padding-bottom: 1px;
  }
  .ab-link:hover {
    color: var(--paper-soft);
    background: var(--claret);
  }

  /* ─────────── MASTHEAD ─────────── */
  .ab-mast {
    padding: calc(var(--x1) + var(--x2)) 0 var(--x1);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    margin-bottom: var(--x1);
  }
  .ab-mast-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    color: var(--claret);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 var(--x3);
  }
  .ab-mast-h {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 var(--x1);
    text-wrap: balance;
    font-feature-settings: "kern" 1, "liga" 1, "dlig" 1;
  }
  .ab-mast-h em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--claret);
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .ab-mast-lede {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2vw, 1.3rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin: 0 0 var(--x4);
    max-width: 42rem;
  }
  .ab-mast-lede em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--claret);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* Portrait card */
  .ab-portrait {
    margin: var(--x1) 0 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--x3);
  }
  .ab-portrait-frame {
    width: 140px;
    height: 140px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(155deg, var(--paper-deep) 0%, var(--paper-warm) 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule-strong);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(15, 14, 14, 0.08);
  }
  .ab-portrait-init {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 5rem;
    color: var(--claret);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }
  .ab-portrait-stamp {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 8px;
    right: 10px;
    font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 8.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    color: var(--claret);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .ab-portrait-cap {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-fainter);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* ─────────── SECTIONS ─────────── */
  .ab-section {
    padding: calc(var(--x1) + var(--x3)) 0 var(--x1);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .ab-section:last-of-type {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .ab-section-head {
    margin-bottom: var(--x1);
  }
  .ab-section-label {
    font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    color: var(--claret);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 var(--x4);
  }
  .ab-section-h {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
  .ab-section-h em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--claret);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ─────────── PROSE ─────────── */
  .ab-prose {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink);
    max-width: 38rem;
  }
  .ab-prose p {
    margin: 0 0 var(--x4);
  }
  .ab-prose em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--claret);
  }
  .ab-prose .ab-link em {
    color: inherit;          /* don't double-color links inside italics */
  }
  .ab-aphorism {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--claret);
    text-align: center;
    margin: calc(var(--x1) + var(--x4)) 0;
    padding: var(--x4) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  /* ─────────── TIMELINE ─────────── */
  .ab-timeline {
    margin: calc(var(--x1) + var(--x4)) 0 0;
    padding: var(--x1) 0 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .ab-timeline-label {
    font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    color: var(--claret);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 var(--x4);
  }
  .ab-timeline-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--rule-strong);
  }
  .ab-timeline-list li {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 7rem 1fr;
    gap: var(--x3);
    padding: var(--x4) var(--x3);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    position: relative;
    transition: background 0.2s ease;
  }
  .ab-timeline-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .ab-timeline-list li::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: -4px;
    top: 50%;
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid var(--claret);
    transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(45deg);
  }
  .ab-timeline-list li:hover {
    background: var(--paper-soft);
  }
  .ab-time-year {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--claret);
    font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .ab-time-event {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  /* ─────────── CONNECT ─────────── */
  .ab-connect-deck {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin: 0 0 var(--x1);
    max-width: 38rem;
  }
  .ab-connect-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .ab-connect-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: var(--x3) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--ink);
    transition: color 0.2s ease, padding 0.2s ease;
  }
  .ab-connect-list li:last-child .ab-connect-link {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .ab-connect-link:hover {
    color: var(--claret);
    padding-left: 10px;
  }
  .ab-connect-name {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .ab-connect-name em {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--claret);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-left: 6px;
  }
  .ab-connect-arrow {
    font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--ink-fainter);
    transition: transform 0.25s ease, color 0.25s ease;
  }
  .ab-connect-link:hover .ab-connect-arrow {
    transform: translateX(6px);
    color: var(--claret);
  }

  /* ─────────── BUILDS (Skills / Scroll / Workshop) ─────────── */
  .ab-builds-deck {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin: 0 0 var(--x1);
    max-width: 42rem;
  }
  .ab-builds-deck em {
    color: var(--claret);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .ab-builds {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--x3);
  }
  .ab-build {
    background: var(--paper-soft);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: var(--x3) var(--x3) var(--x3);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--ink);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
    transition: border-color 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
  }
  .ab-build:hover {
    border-color: var(--ink);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(15, 14, 14, 0.10);
  }
  .ab-build--featured {
    background: var(--paper-deep);
    border-color: var(--claret);
    border-width: 1px;
    border-top-width: 3px;
  }
  .ab-build-ribbon {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--claret);
    color: var(--paper-soft);
    font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.26em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .ab-build-num {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--claret);
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 0 0 var(--x4);
    font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums;
  }
  .ab-build-h {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 var(--x4);
  }
  .ab-build-deck {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin: 0 0 var(--x3);
    flex: 1;
  }
  .ab-build-deck em { font-style: italic; color: var(--claret); }
  .ab-build-cta {
    font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--claret);
    margin-top: auto;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    transition: gap 0.25s ease;
  }
